msgctxt "7884"
msgid "Hamazaki"
msgstr "Hamazaki"

msgctxt "7888"
msgid "Kiryu"
msgstr "Kiryu"

msgctxt "7892"
msgid "Talk_Yes"
msgstr "Talk_Yes"

msgctxt "7896"
msgid "Woman"
msgstr "Mujer"

msgctxt "7900"
msgid "Yasuko"
msgstr "Yasuko"

msgctxt "7904"
msgid "Talk_No"
msgstr "Talk_No"

msgctxt "68_Hamazaki"
msgid "The heck is this place, Kiryu?"
msgstr "The heck is this place, Kiryu?"

msgctxt "80_Kiryu"
msgid "The ex-hideout of a family called the Tamashiro I crossed\\r\n"\n"swords with last year. It's been empty for a while now."
msgstr "El antiguo escondite de una familia llamada Tamashiro con\\r la que me enfrenté el año pasado. Lleva vacío un tiempo."

msgctxt "92_Kiryu"
msgid "If there's anywhere we won't be interrupted, it's here."
msgstr "If there's anywhere we won't be interrupted, it's here."

msgctxt "152_Kiryu"
msgid "So are you ready to talk?"
msgstr "So are you ready to talk?"

msgctxt "164_Kiryu"
msgid "We might be able to find where your brother is if we pool\\r\n"\n"all the information we have."
msgstr "We might be able to find where your brother is if we pool\\r\n"\n"all the information we have."

msgctxt "176_Woman"
msgid "Right..."
msgstr "Cierto..."

msgctxt "188_Kiryu"
msgid "Now, you said you were Taiga Saejima's sister?"
msgstr "Now, you said you were Taiga Saejima's sister?"

msgctxt "200_Woman"
msgid "That's right. My name is Yasuko Saejima."
msgstr "That's right. My name is Yasuko Saejima."

msgctxt "212_Yasuko"
msgid "I... haven't seen my brother for twenty-five years now."
msgstr "I... haven't seen my brother for twenty-five years now."

msgctxt "224_Yasuko"
msgid "Every single day, I tried to visit him in prison... but they\\r\n"\n"never once let me in to see him. Not a single time in all\\r\n"\n"those years."
msgstr "Every single day, I tried to visit him in prison... but they\\r\n"\n"never once let me in to see him. Not a single time in all\\r\n"\n"those years."

msgctxt "236_Yasuko"
msgid "Then just a few days ago, I heard he was being transferred."
msgstr "Then just a few days ago, I heard he was being transferred."

msgctxt "248_Yasuko"
msgid "To Penitentiary No. 2 down in Okinawa."
msgstr "To Penitentiary No. 2 down in Okinawa."

msgctxt "260_Hamazaki"
msgid "Hm..."
msgstr "Mm..."

msgctxt "272_Yasuko"
msgid "As soon as they told me, I left Kamurocho and raced down\\r\n"\n"here."
msgstr "As soon as they told me, I left Kamurocho and raced down\\r\n"\n"here."

msgctxt "284_Yasuko"
msgid "But no matter how many times I ask, all the authorities\\r\n"\n"insist such a place has never existed."
msgstr "But no matter how many times I ask, all the authorities\\r\n"\n"insist such a place has never existed."

msgctxt "296_Kiryu"
msgid "That's what we walked in on."
msgstr "That's what we walked in on."

msgctxt "308_Yasuko"
msgid "Yes. I'm at my wit's end here."
msgstr "Yes. I'm at my wit's end here."

msgctxt "320_Hamazaki"
msgid "...Yasuko-san, yeah?"
msgstr "...Yasuko-san, yeah?"

msgctxt "332_Hamazaki"
msgid "Anyone who told you Penitentiary No. 2 doesn't exist either\\r\n"\n"doesn't know the truth or was lying to you. It's real, all right."
msgstr "Anyone who told you Penitentiary No. 2 doesn't exist either\\r\n"\n"doesn't know the truth or was lying to you. It's real, all right."

msgctxt "344_Yasuko"
msgid "What!?"
msgstr "¡¿Qué?!"

msgctxt "356_Hamazaki"
msgid "I should know. I've been there."
msgstr "I should know. I've been there."

msgctxt "368_Yasuko"
msgid "You have!?"
msgstr "You have!?"

msgctxt "380_Hamazaki"
msgid "Oh yeah. They gave it some fancy name and number like a\\r\n"\n"regular old prison, but it's not actually government-run. You\\r\n"\n"ever hear of a private prison?"
msgstr "Oh yeah. They gave it some fancy name and number like a\\r\n"\n"regular old prison, but it's not actually government-run. You\\r\n"\n"ever hear of a private prison?"

msgctxt "392_Yasuko"
msgid "Of course. And that's what Penitentiary No. 2 is?"
msgstr "Of course. And that's what Penitentiary No. 2 is?"

msgctxt "404_Hamazaki"
msgid "Yup. Details are gonna have to come later, though. I've got\\r\n"\n"some more important news for you first. Truth of the matter\\r\n"\n"is... I know your brother."
msgstr "Yup. Details are gonna have to come later, though. I've got\\r\n"\n"some more important news for you first. Truth of the matter\\r\n"\n"is... I know your brother."

msgctxt "416_Yasuko"
msgid "You know Taiga!?"
msgstr "You know Taiga!?"

msgctxt "428_Hamazaki"
msgid "Mhm. Oh, and here's another grain of truth for you. He's\\r\n"\n"long gone from Okinawa."
msgstr "Mhm. Oh, and here's another grain of truth for you. He's\\r\n"\n"long gone from Okinawa."

msgctxt "440_Hamazaki"
msgid "Probably reached Kamurocho by now if I had to guess. Me and\\r\n"\n"him broke out together a few days ago."
msgstr "Probably reached Kamurocho by now if I had to guess. Me and\\r\n"\n"him broke out together a few days ago."

msgctxt "452_Yasuko"
msgid "You... what?"
msgstr "You... what?"

msgctxt "464_Kiryu"
msgid "He's telling the truth. Your brother washed up at my\\r\n"\n"orphanage the next day, and I ended up giving him some\\r\n"\n"money to get up to Kamurocho."
msgstr "He's telling the truth. Your brother washed up at my\\r\n"\n"orphanage the next day, and I ended up giving him some\\r\n"\n"money to get up to Kamurocho."

msgctxt "476_Kiryu"
msgid "Sorry, Yasuko. You just missed him."
msgstr "Sorry, Yasuko. You just missed him."

msgctxt "488_Yasuko"
msgid "In that case..."
msgstr "In that case..."

msgctxt "500_Yasuko"
msgid "I can't afford to waste any more time here. I need to get\\r\n"\n"back to Kamurocho at once."
msgstr "I can't afford to waste any more time here. I need to get\\r\n"\n"back to Kamurocho at once."

